item.title: REVOLUCION HIP HOP 5TH FESTIVAL GUATEMALA CITY, EL PODCAST! SOMOSHIPHOP.COM
item.description: Somos Hip Hop Radio is Back with the Revolucion Hip Hop Guatemala Festival Podcast! Celebrating the 5th edition of the International Hip Hop Festival for 4 days of non stop Hip Hop In Guatemala City Central AMERICA! IN THIS PODCAST: Hosted By E-LEGAL aka DJ 'E' AND SPIN EL POETA. Music by Spin el Poeta and Most from Code Blue, Interview about his work in Canada, Cuba, Venezuela and Latin America. New Music from Reyes del Bajo Mundo de El Salvador y New York New Hit "Lo que Quisiera" from Grupo Criollo de Republica Dominicana.Also Area 23 from Venezuela, E-LEGAL new Track Latinos Al Poder. Special Interview with LOVEL 2 Member of Bacteria Sound System Crew and Organiser of the Hip Hop Revolucion Festival in Guatemala City. New Music from Bacteria Sound System, Strate Crooked and alot of Sick Hip Hop Related Information about the 5th Hip Hop Revolucion Festival to be celebrated in Guatemala on Dec 2, 3 , 4, 5. in Guatemala City. Bonus Tracks(Sneak Preview "Soy Ilegal de E-legal y Spin V y Revolucion Cultural From Strate Crooked, DJ Warlock One, Komandante) at the End of Podcast Straight up Puro Hip Hop! REVOLUCION CULTURAL!

item.title: LA REVOLUCION PODCAST : A MESSAGE TO FAKE ARTISTS AND FAKE RECORD LABELS
item.description: La Revolucion Podcast: A message to Fake wack artists Like: Wisin y Yandel, Daddy Yankee, Don Omar, To Fake ass Record Labels like Machete Music, Punk mothafuka Gustavo Lopez, DJ Cassanova, Universal Music and all those fake ass mothafukas that dont know SHIT about what the fuck REVOLUTIONARY MUSIC REALLY IS. In this Podcast We Have a Line up of Rappers with the Lyrical firing power of a Guatemalan Death Squad and the Mussle of a Guerrilla Movement from Latino America, Also The opinion on the state of the Music Industry Tactiques from Rodstarz de Rebeldiaz, William Dinero de Code Blue, Ephniko from Colombia and Komandante directly from Los Angeles. We Finish this year Triumphant with the Latin Hip Hop Movement on The West Coast, East Coast, Latino America, Cuba, Puerto Rico as ONE Block of artists with the same purposse, mission and Unified with the intention of making Musica Revolucionaria y Musica de Calle de Verdad!
